rom the inhuman invasion journeying through hidden worlds and colorful dimensions.","genre_ids":[28,12,10751,14,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.5986,"vote_count":142,"poster_path":"/x2n0On0tEvlPiXVqajPYbPYJtn0.jpg","release_date":"2019-02-05","vote_average":5.6,"backdrop_path":"/nkLt5EEHWDTMbmUX5rj4fMcvI0I.jpg","original_title":"神探蒲松齡","original_language":"zh"},{"id":440630,"adult":false,"title":"Ice","video":false,"overview":"Contemporary Russia. Nadya gives up her dream of becoming a champion figure skater when she is hospitalized with an injury. But then she meets Sasha, a hockey player, who decides to teach her to believe in herself and her dream again.","genre_ids":[35,10749,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.0943,"vote_count":119,"poster_path":"/sySCOn2MBNcOy5w4iYYpYgWTcA6.jpg","release_date":"2018-02-14","vote_average":6.853,"backdrop_path":"/gL26uumm6mulHqUkacFm5dLoyPM.jpg","original_title":"Лёд","original_language":"ru"},{"id":567733,"adult":false,"title":"Crypto","video":false,"overview":"A young agent is tasked with investigating a tangled web of corruption and fraud in New York.","genre_ids":[53,80,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.1962,"vote_count":203,"poster_path":"/fzTvnA3buXsjdmjrYRDozKBFF78.jpg","release_date":"2019-04-12","vote_average":5.377,"backdrop_path":"/4XT591GqHTqnhjSPaxlU79CclyP.jpg","original_title":"Crypto","original_language":"en"},{"id":394537,"adult":false,"title":"The Pirates of Somalia","video":false,"overview":"After an inspiring chance encounter with his idol, rookie journalist Jay Bahadur uproots his life and moves to Somalia looking for the story of a lifetime. Hooking up with a local fixer, he attempts to get embedded with the local Somali pirates, only to quickly find himself in over his head.","genre_ids":[18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.78,"vote_count":246,"poster_path":"/a8dlDPwo9mnorurL6ukIpyHZZd7.jpg","release_date":"2017-12-08","vote_average":6.9,"backdrop_path":"/iUH1dWoIR1eoE6sEzwhH49T0sE