hal","original_language":"en"},{"id":249021,"adult":false,"title":"Android Cop","video":false,"overview":"In the year 2045, a Los Angeles Police Department detective and his new android partner enter the Zone, a forbidden section of the city plagued with an unknown disease. There, they discover the source of the illness and attempt to stop it using the android's advanced technology and weaponry.","genre_ids":[28,878],"popularity":0.6339,"vote_count":73,"poster_path":"/pStgVcVSMNDykydPzMTuAiXAb50.jpg","release_date":"2014-02-04","vote_average":3.986,"backdrop_path":"/9DYCjWFD9iw5S7uunqqBj7lx77b.jpg","original_title":"Android Cop","original_language":"en"},{"id":772445,"adult":false,"title":"Jezabel","video":false,"overview":"Four upper-class high school students live carefree between drugs, games and love until one of the girls, Eli, is brutally killed. Sixteen years later, the memory of the crime torments Alain, another member of the group.","genre_ids":[53,80,9648,878],"popularity":0.8178,"vote_count":23,"poster_path":"/4zBkbAXsx5IUx97ndJm18UoxIKd.jpg","release_date":"2022-03-10","vote_average":5.3,"backdrop_path":"/jvMqAkk1vAkOIJPaWkpMwRia4OC.jpg","original_title":"Jezabel","original_language":"es"},{"id":425906,"adult":false,"title":"The Prototype","video":false,"overview":"A government agent stumbles upon an alien conspiracy to conquer Earth. Using a blue liquid created by the aliens to make soldiers stronger, he becomes The Prototype-the only hope for mankind.","genre_ids":[28,878,53],"popularity":0.9058,"vote_count":22,"poster_path":"/gGDDRopgIQhemPJ04eI0r0FfmIt.jpg","release_date":"2022-02-25","vote_average":4.3,"backdrop_path":"/21Pj94MOsW5708QTSwRZea8ddfo.jpg","original_title":"The Prototype","original_language":"en"},{"id":428862,"adult":false,"title":"Mobile Suit Gundam: The Origin V: Clash at Loum","video":false,"overview":"Universal Century 0079. Humanity has turned even space itself into a battlefield, and the Principality of Zeon forces advance after 